item.title: How can i make it infinite health?
item.dc:creator: @Jordanz_Pk Jordanz Pk
item.description:
@Jordanz_Pk wrote:

First make sure that you are logged off.

Now go to your ‘characters’ file and search your name (or the name you want to infinate health on) and find

character-skill = 3

And change the number next to it to a high number (but make sure its under 2B, over 1K)
Then save,
And you got infinate health.
